msgid ""
"Run consent + blocking for logged-in users too (off = logged-in users see "
"the unmodified site)"
msgstr ""
"Appliquer le consentement et le blocage aussi aux utilisateurs connectés "
"(désactivé = les utilisateurs connectés voient le site non modifié)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:112
msgid "Respect DNT / GPC"
msgstr "Respecter DNT / GPC"

#: views/admin-settings.php:113
msgid ""
"Treat a Do-Not-Track / Global-Privacy-Control browser signal as a refusal of "
"optional cookies"
msgstr ""
"Traiter un signal de navigateur Do-Not-Track / Global-Privacy-Control comme "
"un refus des cookies optionnels"

#: views/admin-settings.php:114
msgid "…and hide the banner entirely for those visitors (otherwise still ask)"
msgstr ""
"…et masquer entièrement la bannière pour ces visiteurs (sinon, demander "
"quand même)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:117
msgid "Proof of consent"
msgstr "Preuve de consentement"

#: views/admin-settings.php:119
msgid "Store proof of consent"
msgstr "Stocker la preuve de consentement"

#: views/admin-settings.php:120
msgid ""
"Record each consent decision in the database (advised for GDPR "
"accountability)"
msgstr ""
"Enregistrer chaque décision de consentement dans la base de données "
"(conseillé pour la responsabilité RGPD)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:122
msgid "IP address"
msgstr "Adresse IP"

#: views/admin-settings.php:122
msgid ""
"A salted hash is irreversible but still lets you count unique consents. Your "
"server already logs IPs; GDPR requires disclosing it, not omitting it."
msgstr ""
"Un hachage salé est irréversible tout en vous permettant de comptabiliser "
"les consentements uniques. Votre serveur enregistre déjà les IP ; le RGPD "
"exige de le divulguer, pas de l’omettre."

#: views/admin-settings.php:124
msgid "Store a salted hash (recommended)"
msgstr "Stocker un hachage salé (recommandé)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:124
msgid "Store the full IP"
msgstr "Stocker l’IP complète"

#: views/admin-settings.php:128
msgid "Store user-agent"
msgstr "Stocker le user-agent"

#: views/admin-settings.php:129
msgid "Record the browser user-agent string"
msgstr "Enregistrer la chaîne user-agent du navigateur"

#: views/admin-settings.php:131
msgid "Store WP user"
msgstr "Stocker l’utilisateur WP"

#: views/admin-settings.php:132
msgid "Record the logged-in user (guests are never identified)"
msgstr ""
"Enregistrer l’utilisateur connecté (les invités ne sont jamais identifiés)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:134
msgid "Log retention (days)"
msgstr "Conservation du journal (jours)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:135
msgid "0 = keep forever"
msgstr "0 = conserver indéfiniment"

#: views/admin-settings.php:136
msgid ""
"Proof of consent should be kept at least as long as the consent lasts (the "
"consent duration above) — otherwise you may delete evidence for consents "
"that are still valid."
msgstr ""
"La preuve de consentement doit être conservée au moins aussi longtemps que "
"le consentement (la durée de consentement ci-dessus) — sinon vous risquez de "
"supprimer des preuves pour des consentements encore valides."

#: views/admin-settings.php:138
msgid "On uninstall"
msgstr "À la désinstallation"

#: views/admin-settings.php:138
msgid ""
"Deleting the plugin normally removes everything, including the consent log. "
"Keep it if you may need the proof of consent after uninstalling (legal "
"accountability) — re-installing later will reuse it."
msgstr ""
"Supprimer l’extension efface normalement tout, y compris le journal de "
"consentement. Conservez-le si vous pourriez avoir besoin de la preuve de "
"consentement après la désinstallation (responsabilité légale) — une "
"réinstallation ultérieure le réutilisera."

#: views/admin-settings.php:139
msgid "Keep the consent log (proof of consent) when uninstalling"
msgstr "Conserver le journal de consentement (preuve de consentement) à la désinstallation"

#: views/admin-settings.php:147 views/admin-settings.php:273
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Texte"

#: views/admin-settings.php:148
msgid "Presets"
msgstr "Préréglages"

